1 information we collect we collect information necessary to provide and improve our services this includes information you provide directly to us and information collected automatically when you use atlantic server services personal information full name and contact details email address phone number billing and payment information handled securely by payment processors account details username password any communications or feedback you provide to us technical information ip address and device identifiers server logs and usage data browser type and operating system performance and diagnostic data 2 how we use your information we use your information to provide operate and maintain our services process orders and manage billing improve user experience and develop new features communicate with you regarding updates security alerts and support protect against fraud and ensure service security comply with legal obligations 3 sharing of information we do not sell or rent your personal information we may share your data only in these circumstances service providers we share information with trusted partners who perform services such as payment processing technical support and analytics legal compliance we may disclose your information if required by law legal processes or to protect the rights and safety of atlantic server our users or others 4 data security we take data security seriously and implement various measures to protect your information including encryption for data in transit and at rest regular security monitoring and vulnerability assessments strict access controls and authentication procedures staff training and security awareness programs 5 data retention we retain personal information as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy comply with legal obligations and resolve disputes when no longer needed data is securely deleted or anonymized 6 your rights depending on your jurisdiction you may have rights to access your personal data request correction of incorrect or incomplete data request deletion of your personal data object to or restrict certain data processing request data portability to exercise these rights please contact us using the details provided below 7 cookies and tracking we use cookies and similar technologies to improve our services and analyze usage you can control or disable cookies via your browser settings but this may impact your experience 8 international transfers your information may be transferred to and processed in other countries we take steps to ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with applicable laws 9 children s privacy atlantic server services are not directed to children under 13 we do not knowingly collect personal information from children if we learn that we have collected such data we will take steps to delete it promptly 10 updates to privacy policy we may update this privacy policy periodically we will notify you of significant changes by posting the updated policy on this page and updating the last updated date 11 contact us if you have questions or concerns about this privacy policy please contact
